00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:16,520
Vui quá đi mất!

332
00:24:21,670 --> 00:24:23,960
Ta biết bay rồi!

333
00:24:28,090 --> 00:24:28,610
Này,

334
00:24:28,770 --> 00:24:29,370
